'''Alex Moroder''' (* 13. Mei [[1923]] a [[Urtijëi]] [[Südtirol]]; † 11. November [[2006]]  a Urtij<u>ei.</u>
[[File:Radio_Ladin_16-10-57_Alex_y_Bruno.JPG|miniatura|250x250px|Adum cun Bruno Moroder Cunfolia te stua sa Rusina ulache ie nasciú 'l Comité Radio Ladin de Gherdëina.]]
Mut de [[Ludwig Moroder]] y dla scritëura per ladin  [[Adele Moroder]]. 
Tla segonda viëra ie stat saudè pra i Alpini y do 'l 8 de setëmber 1943 iel stat mandà ti ciampes de perjonia tl Reich. <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20160330050403/http://www.lusenberg.com/alex/Alex_interview_ladin.pdf Intervista sul fascism, nazism e sun la viëra cun Ingrid Runggaldier.]</ref>

Ël à maridà tl 1945 Paula Grossrubatscher dl Rusina i abu cin mutons: Ulrike, Wolfgang [[Egon Moroder-Rusina|Egon]], Ruth y Stefan. <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20091026133634/http://www.lusenberg.com/alex/curriculum.html Autobiografia]</ref> 

Alex ie stat fundadëur adum cun Bruno Moroder dla [[Radio Ladin de Gherdëina]] tl 1955, tl 1958 fundadëur cun Robert presidënt, Hermann Moroder-Jumbierch, Heinrich Moroder-Doss, Raimund Mureda, Luis Piazza, Vigil Prugger  dl [[Museum de Gherdëina]] tl 1958.  Ël ie stat ncé per truepes ani aministradëur dla [[La Usc di Ladins|Usc di Ladins]] y dla [[Cësa di Ladins]] a Urtijëi.

